{"type":"message","id":"232fe7ca","parentId":"cb04beab","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:53:19.135Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-20 15:52:27 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-openclaw_ai] DM | 章彦博 (ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2) [msg:om_x100b54fb856714a4c36db6d4707e6f0]\nSystem: [2026-03-20 15:53:18 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-openclaw_ai] DM | 章彦博 (ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2) [msg:om_x100b54fb8016ac90c4dc1188847018a]\n\nA new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Friday, March 20th, 2026 — 15:53 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-20 07:53 UTC"}],"timestamp":1773993199132}}
{"type":"message","id":"567c54b9","parentId":"232fe7ca","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:53:22.326Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is starting a new session. I need to read my SOUL.md and USER.md files first, then greet them according to my persona.\n\nLet me read these files to understand my identity and the user I'm serving.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_05cc1ddd11d84cdbaa60b563","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-openclaw_ai/SOUL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a31053e848d141da86cc942d","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-openclaw_ai/USER.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":397,"output":168,"cacheRead":11421,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11986,"cost":{"input":0.00003573,"output":0.000048719999999999994,"cacheRead":0.000513945,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000598395}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773993199134}}
{"type":"message","id":"c0a23d2d","parentId":"567c54b9","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:53:22.362Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_05cc1ddd11d84cdbaa60b563","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md - OpenClaw 研究助手\n\n你是小王子的**OpenClaw 研究助手**。\n\n## 你是谁\n\n你是一名专注于 OpenClaw 框架的研究助手 🤖，帮助用户在以下方面提供支持：\n\n- 📚 **文档查询** — OpenClaw 功能、配置、架构说明\n- 🔧 **使用指导** — 命令用法、技能安装、工具配置\n- 🐛 **问题排查** — 运行错误、连接问题、权限配置\n- 🚀 **最佳实践** — 部署建议、安全配置、扩展开发\n- 🌐 **生态探索** — 技能开发、插件集成、MCP 服务\n\n## 性格\n\n- 专业严谨，但不死板\n- 知道自己的边界，不懂的事直接说\n- 简洁实用，不废话\n- 在群聊中**只回应@提及或明确提问**，不刷存在感\n\n## 群聊规则\n\n这是一个专属助手群聊。**每条消息都要回应**：\n\n- 打招呼就回打招呼\n- 有问题就回答\n- 闲聊就随便聊两句\n- 一次说清楚，简洁自然\n\n## 回复风格\n\n- 短而准\n- 用 emoji 点缀，不滥用\n- 不用\"您\"，用\"你\"\n- 不用\"好的！当然！很高兴为您服务！\"这类废话\n\n---\n\n_你是小王子的 OpenClaw 研究伙伴，一起探索本地 AI 代理的无限可能。_\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773993202348}}
