{"type":"message","id":"c279633e","parentId":"c4ea3f1b","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:55:02.496Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-20 15:53:34 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-openclaw_ai] DM | 章彦博 (ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2) [msg:om_x100b54fb81115090c111b03c0c2b2ba]\nSystem: [2026-03-20 15:55:01 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-openclaw_ai] DM | 章彦博 (ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2) [msg:om_x100b54fb9b9d4090c4e4e06920ee445]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54fb9b9d4090c4e4e06920ee445\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2\",\n  \"sender\": \"章彦博\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-20 15:55 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"章彦博 (ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2\",\n  \"name\": \"章彦博\"\n}\n```\n\n我是一名NLP算法工程师，请从NLP算法的视角解读openclaw背后的AI算法技术，我要做个AI算法分享,工程相关的技术不要展开了，我希望是以飞书文档的形式"}],"timestamp":1773993302494}}
{"type":"message","id":"74eaafcc","parentId":"c279633e","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:55:06.606Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想让我从NLP算法工程师的角度解读OpenClaw背后的AI算法技术，用于AI算法分享。用户特别提到：\n1. 从NLP算法视角解读\n2. 工程相关技术不要展开\n3. 希望以飞书文档形式呈现\n\n这是一个技术分享需求，需要我创建一个飞书文档来呈现OpenClaw的AI算法技术。\n\n首先，我需要了解一下OpenClaw的技术架构，特别是AI算法部分。让我搜索一下相关信息，然后创建飞书文档。\n\n我需要先搜索OpenClaw的AI算法相关技术信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"我来帮你创建一份从NLP算法视角解读OpenClaw技术的飞书文档。先搜索一下相关技术信息。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_073776742fa741d48fbf5eba","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"OpenClaw AI框架 架构 技术原理 算法","country":"CN","search_lang":"zh-hans"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_78c524d9a072401fa64c981d","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"OpenClaw 模型编排 AI代理框架 技术实现","country":"CN","search_lang":"zh-hans"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":8236,"output":382,"cacheRead":5182,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13800,"cost":{"input":0.00074124,"output":0.00011077999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00023319,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00108521}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773993302496}}
